name: Luke Skywalker - Faithful Friend
extDescription:
Action [1, T]: Give a Shield token to a [Heroism] unit you played this phase. Epic Action: If you control 6 or more resources, deploy this leader. (Flip him, ready him, and move him to the ground arena.)

[Deployed Leader Unit]
On Attack: You may give another unit a Shield token.

name: Darth Vader - Dark Lord of the Sith
cleanName: Darth Vader Dark Lord of the Sith
extDescription:
Action [1, T]: If you played a [Villainy] card this phase, deal 1 damage to a unit and 1 damage to a base. Epic Action: If you control 7 or more resources, deploy this leader. (Flip him, ready him, and move him to the ground arena.)

[Deployed Leader Unit]
On Attack: You may deal 2 damage to a unit.

name: Moff Gideon - Formidable Commander (Hyperspace)
extDescription:
Action [T]: Attack with a unit that costs 3 or less. If it's attacking a unit, it gets +1/+0 for this attack. Epic Action: If you control 5 or more resources, deploy this leader. (Flip him, ready him, and move him to the ground arena.)
[Deployed Leader Unit]
Overwhelm (When attacking an enemy unit, deal excess damage to the opponent's base.)
Each friendly unit that costs 3 or less gets +1/+0 and gains Overwhelm while attacking an enemy unit.

name: The Mandalorian - Sworn To The Creed (Hyperspace)
cleanName: The Mandalorian Sworn To The Creed Hyperspace
extDescription:
When you play an upgrade: You may exhaust this leader. If you do, exhaust an enemy unit with 4 or less remaining HP. Epic Action: If you control 6 or more resources, deploy this leader. (Flip him, ready him, and move him to the ground arena.)
[Deployed Leader Unit]
When you play an upgrade: You may exhaust an enemy unit with 6 or less remaining HP
